      <title>墨西哥计划推出近岸外包激励措施以抑制中国进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/mexico-plans-nearshoring-incentives-in-bid-to-curb-china-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆宣布了一项减少该国从中国进口的计划，以支持本土产业并与美国和加拿大结盟，成为其贸易伙伴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/mexico-plans-nearshoring-incentives-in-bid-to-curb-china-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 18:38:21 GMT</pubDate>
